<p>GHK-Cu is one of those <a href="/articles/what-are-peptides-beginners-guide">peptides</a> that sounds too good to be true. A tiny tripeptide that boosts collagen, speeds wound healing, regrows <a href="/articles/ghk-cu-skin-hair-guide">hair</a>, and reduces inflammation?</p>

<p>But the research goes back decades, and it holds up surprisingly well. This is one of the few peptides where the clinical data actually matches the hype.</p>

<div class="d">
