  <p>This is an educational breakdown of GHK-Cu covering its mechanisms, clinical evidence, dosing methods, and safety profile. It is <strong>not a recommendation to use GHK-Cu</strong>. Consult a qualified healthcare provider before starting any peptide protocol.</p>
